Fibre reinforced calcium sulfate raised access floor panels by Lindner can be fitted in different areas: heavy-duty, acoustically optimized, and for underfloor heating and cooling. Lindner non-combustible acoustic panels provide protection against fire, noise, corrosion, radiation, or intrusion. The Lindner floors find their application in industrial facilities, workplaces, utility rooms, retail premises, subway or trains stations, stadiums, and concert halls. Lindner floors are protected by the industry specification, standards, and requirements, worldwide.